{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-markdown-remark-frontmatter-slug-js","path":"/blog/delete-facebook/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Himanshu Mishra (@OrkoHunter)","description":"Personal website and blog of Himanshu Mishra (@OrkoHunter)","author":"@OrkoHunter","siteUrl":"https://orkohunter.net"}},"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p><img src=\"./deleted.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>After letting Facebook Inc. build a vast profile of me for 9 years, I deleted my facebook account. Privacy is not my <em>only</em> concern, but I <a href=\"https://medium.com/@OrkoHunter/the-discovery-of-pseudo-acquaintance-9f903601d916\">personally reacted</a> to how Facebook has affected <a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2017/12/20/16800842/facebook-2017-russia-scandal-news-feed-criticism-defectors\">the way we interact in our real life</a>.</p>\n<h3 id=\"how\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#how\" aria-label=\"how permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How?</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Downloaded a copy of my data from facebook -> settings\nThis contained all of my messages, photos, videos, and probably a lot more information which I can not consciously recall sharing with Facebook.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Created a dummy facebook account* and added it to the resourceful groups I might miss out important information from.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p><em>*An account without any interaction i.e. No likes, No reactions neither love nor angry, no comments, no photos/videos, no “friends”. A profile to just receive information on email (sent by facebook).</em></p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/help/delete_account\">https://www.facebook.com/help/delete_account</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>(Going extreme) Blocked Facebook servers on my computer that my computer can never communicate to domain names linked to Facebook servers. See <a href=\"https://github.com/jmdugan/blocklists/tree/master/corporations/facebook\">the list</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"why\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#why\" aria-label=\"why permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>Why?</strong></h3>\n<h4 id=\"social-concerns\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#social-concerns\" aria-label=\"social concerns permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Social concerns</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>People started using Facebook as LinkedIn by adding Freinds and it blurred the lines of relationships between two individuals — <a href=\"https://medium.com/@OrkoHunter/the-discovery-of-pseudo-acquaintance-9f903601d916\">Article</a></li>\n<li>Real addiction to unreal things — <a href=\"https://youtu.be/3ev7GXzFTPg?t=3m10s\">Video</a></li>\n<li>Facebook (read <em>Social Media</em>) promotes Ignorance by thoughtless comments, replies and reactions</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"privacy-concerns\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#privacy-concerns\" aria-label=\"privacy concerns permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Privacy concerns</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>This will suffice — <a href=\"https://stallman.org/facebook.html\">https://stallman.org/facebook.html</a></li>\n</ul>","timeToRead":1,"frontmatter":{"categories":["Tech","Non-Tech"],"date":"Mar 25, 2018","draft":false,"slug":"/blog/delete-facebook","subtitle":"","summary":"","title":"#DeleteFacebook","image":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"src":"/static/f0d3d55e0329b720331a068b6e7e97fa/497c6/deleted.png"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"id":"f63e11f2-791b-57e4-a1dd-9eb70b55e096","frontmatter__slug":"/blog/delete-facebook","__params":{"frontmatter__slug":"blog"}}},"staticQueryHashes":["764694655"]}